   "source": [
    "# Convert to df with just date and closing price\n",
    "data = df.sort_index(ascending=True, axis=0)\n",
    "new_data = pd.DataFrame(index=range(0,len(df)), columns=['Date', 'Close']) #Initialise new dataframe\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 115,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "for i in range(0,len(data)):\n",
    "    new_data['Date'][i] = data['Date'][i]\n",
    "    new_data['Close'][i] = data['Close'][i]"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 116,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "for i in range(0,len(new_data)):\n",
    "    new_data['Year'] = str(new_data['Date'][0])[0:4]\n",
    "    new_data['Month'] = str(new_data['Date'][0])[6:7]\n",
    "    new_data['mon_fri'] = 0"

    "# Train test split\n",
    "train_data = new_data[:1000]\n",
    "test_data = new_data[1000:]\n"
   ]
  },
  {

   "execution_count": 120,
   "metadata": {},

   "source": [
